    <text id="B0021T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>A Waynesboro resident pleads for food assistance, although his request appears to
                    have been rejected.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">Mr. Jackson</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="-06-15">June the 15th</date>
                        <name type="place">Waynesboro</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I rite to inform you that I am suffering for <orig reg="everything"
                    >evrything</orig> that support life. I have <orig reg="neither">neather</orig>
                    food nor raiment. I have <orig reg="been">bin</orig>
                    <orig reg="begging">beging</orig> for <orig reg="two">too</orig> years and the
                    citizens are getting <orig reg="tired">tyard</orig> of my <orig reg="begging"
                        >beging</orig> and I am <orig reg="very">verry</orig> old and infirm and
                    unless I receive help from you or some other <orig reg="source">souce</orig> I
                    can not possible get along.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>yours respectfully</salute>
                    <signed>Feby Leach</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
